title: Grateful Dead Live at Star Lake Amphitheatre on 1992-06-22
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Loser, Walkin' Blues, It Must Have Been The Roses, Queen Jane Approximately, Ramble On Rose, Beat It On Down The Line, Deal

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias > Fire On The Mountain, Victim Or The Crime > Dark Star* > Drums > Jam > Spanish Jam > The Other One > Stella Blue > Goin' Down The Road Feeling Bad

E: Knockin' On Heaven's Door

* - 2nd Verse Only
